# Project Context — Thinkboard

An affordable, visual AI workspace where creators drag-and-drop YouTube videos, PDFs, images, and voice notes onto a canvas and use AI to research, brainstorm, and write content — all in one place.

## Source of Truth

Read these files before building any feature or screen:

- **Features & scope**: `planning/mvp-plan.md`
- **Screens & interactions**: `planning/ui-plan.md`
- **Design tokens**: `planning/style-guide.md`
- **Dependencies**: `planning/tech-stack.md`

