## Constraints

- Do not add features, screens, or routes not defined in the planning docs.
- Do not add npm packages not listed in `planning/tech-stack.md` without explicit approval.
- Free tier: 3 boards, 30 AI messages/day, YouTube + PDF + text only, GPT-4o mini.
- Pro tier: Unlimited boards, 200 AI messages/day, all input types, GPT-4o.
